org.springframework.http

接口 StreamingHttpOutputMessage

  • 所有超级接口:
    HttpMessage, HttpOutputMessage

    public interface StreamingHttpOutputMessage
extends HttpOutputMessage
    Represents a HTTP output message that allows for setting a streaming body. Note that such messages typically do not support HttpOutputMessage.getBody() access.
    从以下版本开始:
    4.0
    另请参阅:
